{"id":102,"name":"التكاثر","transliteration":"At-Takathur","translation":"The Rivalry in world increase","type":"meccan","total_verses":8,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translation":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you"},{"id":2,"text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","translation":"Until you visit the graveyards"},{"id":3,"text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"No! You are going to know"},{"id":4,"text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"Then no! You are going to know"},{"id":5,"text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty"},{"id":6,"text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","translation":"You will surely see the Hellfire"},{"id":7,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty"},{"id":8,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translation":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure"}]}
